# ============================================================================
# .env.example — Environment variable template for the Legacy Business-Rule
# Extraction Agent Network.
#
# WHAT THIS FILE DOES:
#   Shows you which environment variables the project needs. Copy this to .env
#   and fill in your real API key. The .env file is git-ignored so your secret
#   stays local.
#
# HOW TO USE:
#   1. Copy this file:  cp .env.example .env
#   2. Replace the placeholder below with your actual Google Gemini API key.
#   3. Never commit .env to version control.
# ============================================================================

# Google Gemini API key — required for the LLM agents (Business Rule Extractor,
# Migration Risk Assessor, Spec Generator). Get one at:
# https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GOOGLE_API_KEY=your-google-api-key-here
